    <h3 id="1.1" style="font-weight: bold; color: black;">1.1 How to Return a Borrowed Mug</h3>
    <p style="text-align:justify">
        <ol style="margin-left: 2em;">
            <li>Click the blue ‘Mug Return’ button to open a modal window.</li>
            <li>Make sure that the RFID reader is plugged into one of the USB ports on your PC.</li>
            <li>Click the ‘Scan RFID’ button and proceed to scan the bottom of the mug on the RFID reader.</li>
            <li>Click the blue ‘Process Return’ button to update the database to say that the mug has been returned, and clear the associated user’s rental status.</li>
        </ol>
        *Note: the ‘Cancel’ button or ‘X’ button in the top right can be pressed at anytime to close the modal.
    </p>

    <h3 id="1.2" style="font-weight: bold; color: black;">1.2 How to View the Program’s Monthly Statistics Chart</h3>
