        <ol style="margin-left: 2em;">
            <li>Click the blue ‘Monthly Statistics’ button at the bottom left of the page to open a modal containing the monthly statistics chart of the program.</li>
            <li>Click the ‘X’ button in the top right when you are done viewing the monthly statistics chart in order to close the modal.</li>
        </ol>
    </p>

    <h3 id="1.3" style="font-weight: bold; color: black;">1.3 How to View the Program’s Yearly Statistics Chart</h3>
